<h2>Your Bevgo Seller Account Is Ready</h2>

<p>Hi <%= vendorName %>,</p>

<p>
Thanks for registering as a Bevgo seller. Your vendor profile has been created successfully and your marketplace access is now active.
</p>

<p>
You can now access your seller tools, manage your catalogue, and prepare to receive marketplace orders.
</p>

<ul>
  <li><strong>Vendor name:</strong> <%= vendorName %></li>
  <li><strong>Base location:</strong> <%= baseLocation %></li>
  <li><strong>Category:</strong> <%= categoryTitle %></li>
  <% if (subCategory) { %>
    <li><strong>Sub category:</strong> <%= subCategory %></li>
  <% } %>
</ul>

<p style="margin-top: 16px;">
You can sign in to Bevgo at any time to access your seller dashboard.
</p>

<p style="margin-top: 20px;">
Cheers,<br/>
The Bevgo Team
</p>
